stantially improves both macro and micro F1, from 10.4 to\n14.6 and from 58.2 to 59.1, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Nov 2022 22:10:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 15:49:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
