orithmic fairness, as well as explainable\nAI; and sustainability. I propose to jump-start sustainable AI regulation via\nsustainability impact assessments in the AI Act and sustainable design defects\nin the liability regime. In this way, the law may help spur not only fair AI\nand XAI, but potentially also sustainable AI (SAI).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Nov 2022 09:08:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2022 18:11:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 09:36:04 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2023 12:36:52 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2023 11:57:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-24"}
