t with the scattering\nproblem, we also derive the extrapolated scattering angles for aligned spins.\nOur completion of the Poincar\\'e algebra provides the strongest validation of\nour most comprehensive new results, and thus that the 5PN order has now been\nestablished as the new precision frontier.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Nov 2022 10:50:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Apr 2023 23:18:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-20"}
