 the flamelet types. We conclude that, overall, ChemTab\nDeep Ensembles allows for a more accurate representation of the source energy\nand key species source terms, compared to the model without these\nmodifications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Nov 2022 13:30:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-28"}
